### Frontend – Live Feed Component

#### [NEW] `frontend/src/components/LiveFeed.jsx`
A self-contained component that:
- Fetches `GET /api/notifications` with auth token on mount
- Polls every **15 seconds** via `setInterval`
- Shows unread count badge
- Has "Mark all read" button
- Formats each notification with an icon by `type`, relative timestamp, and read/unread styling
- Shows a skeleton loader during the first fetch

#### [MODIFY] [Dashboard.jsx](file:///c:/Users/User/Desktop/dp%20project%20work/CampusConnect/frontend/src/pages/Dashboard.jsx)
Replace the current hardcoded static feed section (lines 297–389) with `<LiveFeed />`.

